{
  "stem": "24130.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, we had a lot of responsibility as very young children because we had a farm, we had cows, and chicken. and-- we had responsibilities to take care, and do the cooking.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had help, but we still had a lot of responsibilities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had not Jewish help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had somebody would come in to do the laundry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't have a washing machine-- we had to do it by hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were children, we couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To clean up once a week the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On Saturday, we had the-- the same girl would come and make fire, and milk the cows, and bring water from the well.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she would-- she did for us-- she helped-- her mother used to work for-- for my grandma.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she worked for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they spoke Yiddish with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They knew how to speak Yiddish, and they even knew how to pray.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She says, come on Chavalah, you get up, wash yourself, already, and start praying so I can give you something to eat.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she says, say it out loud.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She want to see if I'm saying it the right way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we were very close with the peasants there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About my mother's-- not really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he tried to comfort us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes I would say, ask questions my father because he was such a religious man-- how could he do that to us?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, there are certain questions, certain things that we don't ask questions of God.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have to accept, because this is how God wanted it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as a young child, even till this day, it's very hard to accept that God wanted somebody-- wants somebody to suffer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he-- he was a religious man, and he accepted it, that God wanted it this-- this way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Zarcha?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
